

	This is the source and tools/doc for Ubermud.

roadmap::

Makefile	- top-level makefile. builds everything recursively.
btlib		- b+tree library.
doc		- documentation.
include		- include files for all libraries.
main		- main interpreter and compiler source.
obj		- libraries created by the compiler.
regexlib	- regular expression library.
samples		- random bits of U-code.
util		- utilities and misc. stuff.
